data.title: Wikipedia:WikiProject Apple Inc./List
data.text:
List of all project pages. This list was generated using Petscan, and is being used as a way to use the Special:RecentChangesLinked tool to obtain a watchlist of all WikiProject Apple Inc. articles.

The list was generated on 17 March 2023, at 15:39 UTC time, and is not being automatically updated by a bot. To keep the list up to date

access Petscan

enter "WikiProject Apple Inc. articles" in the "Categories" field of the "Categories" tab

check the "Talk" box under Namespaces in the "Page properties" tab

pick the "Change to page/topic" radio button under "Namespaces" in the "Other sources" tab

in the "Output" tab, under "Format", select "Plain text"

Copy the list, paste it into Visual Studio Code, select all, go to the "Selection" menu bar item, then click "Add Cursors to Line Ends", then add ]]. Then press the cmd+"left arrow" keys on Mac (ctrl+left arrow on Windows) to move the cursors to the beginning of each line, and add [[. You've just turned each page into a wikilink. Copy everything, then paste it below, replacing what's already there.

--
